Further information
Our client is a top tier global reinsurer who are aggressively growing their health portfolio, as such they are seeking an experienced actuary to join their health pricing team. Reporting to the Head of Health, this person will form part of a lean team that work with clients across APAC on pricing and product development. We are looking for someone with 10+ years' experience, and in depth knowledge of medical insurance products. Whilst Asian market experience is preferred, international applicants are welcomed. Please get in touch with Toby Weston on +852 5804 90442 or toby.weston@ojassociates.com
Oliver James Associates
